Conflux

Developer

Portal

Developer resources for building on Conflux. By developers, for developers.

Build on Conflux eSpace

Conflux eSpace is a fully EVM-compatible blockchain with much lower gas fee and higher TPS than Ethereum, which can enable developers quick build dApps on it.

Read the Docs

Build on Conflux Core Space

Conflux Core Space is a third-generation decentralized blockchain with ultra-high performance, utilizing an original Tree-Graph ledger structure and the Ghast consensus algorithm. It natively integrates a transaction sponsorship mechanism, offering a novel user experience for both users and developers.

Read the Docs

Conflux Basics

Get started with Conflux Network and understand its unique features. Learn about the protocol's hybrid consensus mechanism and fast finality, and how it differs from other blockchain platforms.

Read the Docs

Run a Node

Learn how to run a node on the Conflux Network and become part of the decentralized network. Follow our step-by-step guides to install and configure your node, connect to the network, and start participating in consensus.

Read the Docs

Mining on Conflux

Learn how to mine CFX on the Conflux Network. Follow our step-by-step guides to install and configure your node, connect to the network, and start mining.
